Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.38,0:00:06.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,05, engage the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.21,0:00:10.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Roger. Prioritizing preservation of civilian life.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.46,0:00:32.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I was their supposed savior, and yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.54,0:00:37.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I was met not with cheers, but with eyes filled\Nwith fear and gandiose expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.25,0:00:38.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.63,0:00:40.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll protect humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.46,0:00:42.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's the whole reason I exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.08,0:00:45.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll protect the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.75,0:00:49.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's all humanity wants from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.42,0:00:53.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's all I live for.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.54,0:00:58.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,A nightmare...
