Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.08,0:02:34.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Talk about a nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.96,0:02:39.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I just know the rest of today's\Ngonna turn out crappy now...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.83,0:02:45.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It comes straight from Queen Echidna:\N"Black Knight Onyx is to report to me at once."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.42,0:02:47.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What? Crap, did she catch on to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.88,0:02:49.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.67,0:02:54.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Lily got real close to revealing\Nmy true identity before, but I dealt with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.38,0:03:00.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You haven't gone to introduce yourself to her yet.\NPerhaps she's angry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.67,0:03:02.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, I haven't done that yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.88,0:03:04.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.00,0:03:08.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I've told her our work has been proceeding\Nsmoothly thanks to Lord Onyx...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.79,0:03:10.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's probably why she wants to see me, you moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.75,0:03:13.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Moron!? Wh-what ELSE was I supposed to tell her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.88,0:03:21.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And Echidna didn't just stumble\Ninto the title of Demon Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.46,0:03:24.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Armed with her beloved Tilving, she can hold\Nher own against Edvard in single combat,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.08,0:03:29.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,and she's as good as a spellcaster as Shutina.\NIt's scary how powerful she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.83,0:03:35.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No matter the tricks I employ,\Nshe might still be able to see through my disguise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.75,0:03:37.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,In any case, you should hurry to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.54,0:03:40.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And if she realizes who you are,\Ncall me without hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.25,0:03:44.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Nah, I'll be fine. I'll figure it out on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.71,0:03:47.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Just pretend you had no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.58,0:03:55.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Right, then, what excuse do I give Echidna?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.75,0:03:59.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Tis I, Black Knight Onyx.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.67,0:04:02.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I have come to answer your summons.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.71,0:04:03.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.08,0:04:06.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Okay, what do you have in store for me,\NDemon Queen Echidna?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.17,0:04:08.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.17,0:04:10.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So you're the wonderful Onyx!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.83,0:04:13.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I've heard all about your marvelous deeds from Shutina!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.79,0:04:15.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry to call you here on short notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.33,0:04:19.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Well... It doesn't sound like she's figured out who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.50,0:04:22.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Please, take a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.54,0:04:26.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wait, hold on. You can't be serious. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.29,0:04:29.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,There are only two seats at this table!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.00,0:04:31.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Come, no need for formalities today!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.79,0:04:35.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Let's enjoy a fine meal and good liquor together!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.96,0:04:40.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Whenever I have a nightmare,\NI know the next day's bound to be hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.75,0:04:45.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Are you drinking, Lord Onyx?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.25,0:04:46.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.17,0:04:50.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I must say, this liquor is incredible.\NNot to mention the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.21,0:04:53.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Excellent!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.50,0:04:58.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,This looks like your typical after-hours drink\Nwith a strait-laced worker and his chill boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.04,0:05:00.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Of course, it's anything but.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.83,0:05:04.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I want to get out of here as quickly as humanly possible,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.33,0:05:08.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,and I'm terrified she'll find out\Nwho I am in the midst of all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.54,0:05:09.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So, Onyx.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.79,0:05:10.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Y-yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.00,0:05:15.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Are you going to wear that helm for much longer?\NWould you please take it off?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.50,0:05:20.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No, I must insist. It would be rude to show\Nmy bare face before you, Your Highness...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.25,0:05:22.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Please, I told you to dispense with formalities.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.83,0:05:26.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And I'd like to be able to talk to you face-to-face!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.21,0:05:27.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.25,0:05:31.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.92,0:05:35.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Now, then, let's see that boorish face of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.83,0:05:36.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.71,0:05:37.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.71,0:05:41.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wait a moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.83,0:05:44.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I didn't have time to change my face that much!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.67,0:05:49.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I-is there something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.13,0:05:54.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I like that stalwart expression!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.00,0:05:57.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I sense great strength behind your soft visage!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.00,0:06:02.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Tis a shame to hide it away behind a helm!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.92,0:06:08.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That was close! Thank goodness she's so drunk...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.33,0:06:11.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Come, now, don't hold back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.58,0:06:14.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Stuff yourself until you burst, by all means!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.88,0:06:19.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm drinking alone with my boss,\Nand if she finds out who I am, I'm dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.50,0:06:21.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,How am I supposed to enjoy my drink like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.71,0:06:26.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Delicious food and liquor!\NThis moment is paradise on Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.08,0:06:30.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I need to get out of this 'paradise' ASAP.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.21,0:06:32.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But I have to be smart and smooth about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.25,0:06:36.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Your Highness, your glass is empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.96,0:06:38.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Allow me to pour you a new drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.92,0:06:41.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you! How considerate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.63,0:06:43.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If you'd allow me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.04,0:06:48.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Let me give you a couple tips about how\Nto make business parties a little easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.21,0:06:53.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Tip #1: The moment your boss' glass is empty, fill it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.83,0:06:56.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Please, have some more.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.08,0:06:56.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I shall!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.13,0:07:00.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You can take a break from the conversation\Nwhile filling their cup,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.04,0:07:02.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,and they'll think you're perceptive and cosiderate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.38,0:07:03.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Here, have another!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.83,0:07:04.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I shall!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.50,0:07:07.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But that's not the only thing I'm after.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.75,0:07:11.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Right now, my goal is simple: get her dead drunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.08,0:07:12.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's all I'm focused on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.42,0:07:14.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,My, you're thirsty! Come, have another!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.75,0:07:15.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I shall!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.08,0:07:20.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,C'mon, drink! Drink 'til you're sloshed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.96,0:07:25.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Then you can put an end to this horrible event!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.54,0:07:33.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Are you quite well, Your Highness?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.50,0:07:35.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Perhaps you've had a bit too much to drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.38,0:07:37.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It may be best if we--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.58,0:07:39.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes, right you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.00,0:07:43.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Now that we're warmed up,\Nlet's go straight for the bottle!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.29,0:07:50.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Come, drink up, Onyx!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.88,0:07:55.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Don't be shy! Chug, chug, chug!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.13,0:07:59.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Though this strategy won't work against\Nheavyweights, so keep THAT in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.08,0:08:06.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's been so long since I've been able\Nto enjoy a relaxing spot of tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.13,0:08:08.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I have Leo to thank for this, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.17,0:08:11.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I wonder how his meeting is going?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.46,0:08:14.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I hope it's all going well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.25,0:08:18.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Perhaps I should go check on them...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.63,0:08:22.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No, what if I say something and only make things worse?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.83,0:08:26.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And why am I getting all worked up over that hero?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.79,0:08:28.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're worried 'bout Leo?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.83,0:08:30.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Here's my report!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.50,0:08:34.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,L-Lily?! Y-you didn't hear anything, all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.38,0:08:37.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You misheard me! That's right,\NI didn't say anything like that at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.71,0:08:40.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh? Say what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.71,0:08:45.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I couldn't kill her with alcohol, but I'm not giving up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.88,0:08:48.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I've got another trick up my sleeve...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.71,0:08:51.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, it'll take some time to execute.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.21,0:08:54.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I just need to segue into it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.79,0:08:58.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I must say, this food is scrumptious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.96,0:09:03.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Especially the sausage you're now eating,\NYour Highness. It's simply to die for.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.33,0:09:05.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You've an eye for quality, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.21,0:09:08.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,There's something in this sausage\Nthat makes it truly fantastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.33,0:09:12.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Tip #2 for making drinking parties less of a headache:
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.46,0:09:17.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,People are fond of those who show\Nan active interest in them and their tastes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.50,0:09:22.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And when you're eating and drinking together,\Nyou have all the fodder you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.75,0:09:27.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,This sausage is made with spices from Largo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.42,0:09:30.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The minced pepper inside gives it\Nsuch a pleasant color, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.08,0:09:31.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Largo, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.00,0:09:34.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We've been hurting for resources so much lately,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.83,0:09:38.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I rarely had time to enjoy such extravagant meals.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.29,0:09:42.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But thanks to Lily's efforts, things are slowly improving.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.21,0:09:45.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I always knew she could handle the task.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.83,0:09:48.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Look at that innocent smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.13,0:09:51.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,She looks like a normal girl when she smiles like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.75,0:09:56.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Of course, I have to give credit to the chefs\Nwho prepared the food so expertly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.71,0:09:59.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You should know that those sausages\Nwere made by yours truly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.00,0:10:04.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The cooks down at the Demon Rat Davern,\Nthe castle dining hall, made absolute slop,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.29,0:10:06.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,so I shared some key recipes and\Ntrained them on how to make them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.63,0:10:13.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Which leads to Tip #3: if there's food,\Nlearn as much as you can about it beforehand!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.25,0:10:17.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And the food topic can lead to any manner\Nof conversation. It's an excellent segue.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.75,0:10:21.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,After what Shutina told me, I was curious\Nabout the kind of man you were...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.96,0:10:24.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But not only are you great at your job,\Nyou're also a culinary expert!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.75,0:10:26.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're quite the man, Lord Onyx!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.83,0:10:30.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hardly, Your Highness. My talents\Nand knowledge are all quite modest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.83,0:10:32.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,There's just one thing I have to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.75,0:10:36.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You seem to always wear that helm of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.21,0:10:39.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I know we touched on this before,\Nbut could you explain why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.83,0:10:41.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.63,0:10:44.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I knew it! Time for Tip #4!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.13,0:10:47.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The only time a powerless newbie\Ncan sell themselves to the boss
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.96,0:10:49.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,is when the boss asks them questions!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.88,0:10:54.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Your answer can drastically change the flow\Nof the outing, or your workload the next day!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.17,0:10:58.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You see, I've been cursed by the goddess Tiana.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.25,0:11:02.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The time I'm allowed to show my face\Nto others is gravely limited.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.67,0:11:05.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,As such, I must spend most\Nof my time encased in armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.00,0:11:10.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Goodness... And you've been without your helm\Nthis whole time. Will you be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.08,0:11:12.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,To be frank, I may be cutting it close.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.42,0:11:18.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But I'm glad to take that risk if it means\Na chance to spend time with Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.54,0:11:22.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, stop. You're quite the talker, aren't you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.04,0:11:24.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And this is how you get out of a drinking excursion early.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.13,0:11:30.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Mention you have a clear-cut time limit,\Nand you can escape any horrific situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.92,0:11:34.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Now Echidna knows I'm working with limited time here...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.63,0:11:37.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What a great day today has been!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.29,0:11:40.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,A toast to the friendship between\NBlack Knight Onyx and Demon Queen Echidna!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.71,0:11:46.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Let us drink and talk the night away!\NDown that bottle, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.25,0:11:51.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Drink the night away? Goodness, I'd be delighted...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.17,0:11:55.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Absolutely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.63,0:11:58.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So you want Leo to have to go away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.88,0:11:59.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.67,0:12:01.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Well?! Do you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.58,0:12:03.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,W-well no, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.42,0:12:05.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,General Shutina! Are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.25,0:12:09.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Dianette? You sound distressed. Is everything all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.21,0:12:11.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I have an extremely urgent message for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.58,0:12:21.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's been a few hours since\Nthis drinking party from hell began,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.50,0:12:26.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,and while she hasn't figured out who I am yet,\NI still want to get the hell out of here...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.67,0:12:30.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Lord Onyx, I'm deeply grateful for all you've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.13,0:12:34.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Not only did you lessen Shutina's workload\Nmere moments after you arrived,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.67,0:12:37.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,but you've also been keeping a watchful eye on Lily.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.75,0:12:40.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Your efforts have been of great help to us all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.38,0:12:43.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I arranged this feast to thank you for your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.96,0:12:45.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Echidna...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.88,0:12:48.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're too kind, Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.21,0:12:53.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Human or demon, we gladly welcome all\Nwho have skills to donate to our cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.92,0:12:57.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm so very glad we have you among\Nour ranks in the Demon Army!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.42,0:12:59.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I see, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.25,0:13:02.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What of that hero, Leo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.00,0:13:06.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I heard he wanted to join. Would you welcome him, to?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.08,0:13:08.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The hero?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.79,0:13:11.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,He's the one exception! I don't want him here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.25,0:13:17.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That twisted man, that social reject!\NHe's the last person I'd want in my army!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.29,0:13:20.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If we were foolish enough to let him join,\Nhe'd destroy us from the inside out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.42,0:13:23.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,He's right here. Literally right in front of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.58,0:13:26.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And he's already made things\NWAY better for your organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.38,0:13:31.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I don't care if he does a thousand,\Nor ten thousand hands' worth of work!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.21,0:13:38.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If it wasn't for that blasted hero,\NI would've had the Philosopher's Stone by now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.13,0:13:40.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So THAT was what she was after.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.46,0:13:42.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's all because of him! All his fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.00,0:13:44.25,Subtitle-2,,0,0,0,,Damn it! Damn it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.21,0:13:46.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Let's leave her to stew and talk\Nabout this Philosopher's Stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.08,0:13:51.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The Philosopher's Stone is a treasure\Nheld in the holy city of Renailles.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.79,0:13:57.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's said that the first saint-king\Ndug it up over 3,000 years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.71,0:14:00.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,then used its power to found the Capital proper.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.25,0:14:05.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Rumors say the Philosopher's Stone turned\Nthe wastelands around the city to green fields,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.17,0:14:12.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,protected the city's people from plague,\Nand could even make someone immortal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.92,0:14:16.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Most of these rumors are bogus, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.83,0:14:21.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,How do I know? Because I've used it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.17,0:14:25.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The Stone in the Capital isn't the one I used, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.46,0:14:31.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But the Philosopher's Stone wouldn't\Ngive someone super powers or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.71,0:14:34.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's not a magic power-up or cure-all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.46,0:14:38.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If you looked up "the worst" in the dictionary,\Nhis name would be there in the definition!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.50,0:14:41.54,Subtitle-2,,0,0,0,,And he'd be in the definition for MORON, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.75,0:14:40.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wait, she's STILL going?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.38,0:14:42.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,How much trash does she have to talk about me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.96,0:14:45.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Do you know how close we were?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.00,0:14:49.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We were so deep into Renailles that\Nwe could see the Stone's sacred hall,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.13,0:14:54.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,and if we'd gotten the Stone,\Nwe could've accomplished all we came for!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.71,0:14:55.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.17,0:14:58.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So the reason you haven't retreated,\Ndespite losing so many men,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.96,0:15:03.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,is because you're not after conquest,\Nbut the Philosopher's Stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.79,0:15:04.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.50,0:15:09.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I was far too aggressive with that war.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.50,0:15:14.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I didn't have to fight all of humanity\Njust to obtain the Philosopher's Stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.96,0:15:17.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Why not deceive them, or steal it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.33,0:15:18.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Or work with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.25,0:15:24.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,There's a children's tale about human\Nand demonkind joining forces, isn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.58,0:15:27.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,"Eibrad, the Joiner of Hands", I believe?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.29,0:15:31.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's an old human story.\NI heard it myself from a succubus storyteller.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.08,0:15:34.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It tells of an oddball imp who travels to the human world
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.75,0:15:38.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,and builds a city where humans\Nand demons live in harmony.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.29,0:15:40.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.71,0:15:43.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But it pales in comparison to our reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.67,0:15:47.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Human and demon are destined\Nto be at odds with one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.63,0:15:49.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The story is just that: a story.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.29,0:15:53.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Which only makes me even\Nmore curious about your goals.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.33,0:15:58.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What do you plan to do with the Philosopher's Stone?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.08,0:16:03.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Ever since her defeat, I've been dying to know...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.92,0:16:09.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,After being beaten into submission,\Nlosing most of her army and territory,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.38,0:16:12.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,why hasn't she returned to the Demon World?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.58,0:16:17.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If she was after something silly\Nlike immortality or riches,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.50,0:16:20.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,she would've lost motivation and left long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.83,0:16:27.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So why does she still persist? Why is she still here\Nin this castle, rebuilding her army?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.63,0:16:28.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.42,0:16:38.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wow... What an incredible view.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.00,0:16:41.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And it's the most beautiful in this light.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.29,0:16:45.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Have you ever been to the Demon World?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.88,0:16:46.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I have not.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.13,0:16:52.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The Demon World, our home, is a grand, vast wasteland.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.33,0:17:00.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It has no sun, no vegetation. The air is heavy,\Nand the water is muddy and impure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.92,0:17:04.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Demon clans fight one another over\Nthe little resources that remain,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.63,0:17:06.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,staining the wasteland with blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.46,0:17:10.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,A demonic world indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.88,0:17:12.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I am sick of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.04,0:17:13.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.00,0:17:17.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I wish to bring order to my world of chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.08,0:17:19.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,To rid the land of conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.00,0:17:25.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,To bathe it in the warm sunlight, to cleanse\Nthe waters to sparkle in that light.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.25,0:17:32.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I wish for fish to swim in those waters, and\Nfor grasslands and forests to sway in the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.13,0:17:39.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That is why I sought the help of Shutina\Nand other skilled comrades:
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.38,0:17:46.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,To come to the human world and retrieve\Nthe Philosopher's Stone to reforge the land.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.58,0:17:47.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I had no idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.67,0:17:57.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,This whole time, she's been fighting humanity\Nto better the lives of her people...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.08,0:18:01.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Surprised to hear these wishes coming\Nfrom the Demon Queen's lips?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.25,0:18:03.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.58,0:18:05.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's all right. I'm accustomed to this reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.25,0:18:12.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I have no quarrel with the humans,\Nbut the Philosopher's Stone will be ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.04,0:18:17.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If they willingly offered it up, then,\Nyou'd accept it without shedding blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.04,0:18:21.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Of course, but even if we explained\Nour good-natured intentions, they wouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.50,0:18:23.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The holy Capital is the center of the human realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.75,0:18:29.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Stealing the very thing that holds that\Ncity together would hurt their livelihoods.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.96,0:18:31.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But that's a sacrifice I'm willing to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.50,0:18:36.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Those who cooperate with us, like the dragonfolk\Nand the humans from Lily's home,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.50,0:18:39.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,will all be given sanctuary in the Demon World,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.96,0:18:42.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,but I care not what happens to the other humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.50,0:18:45.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I don't! Not in the slightest!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.58,0:18:49.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Still, Your Majesty, you've forbidden\Nneedless killing, have you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.50,0:18:53.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is an invasion, but we must\Navoid killing whenever possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.08,0:19:01.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I hear that policy is why the war ended\Nwith mercifully low casualties on both sides.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.13,0:19:06.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And look where that got us: defeat. I curse my naivete.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.88,0:19:10.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I simply could not fully become the villain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.63,0:19:14.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Humans may be our enemy,\Nbut they have homes they want to protect, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.13,0:19:19.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And friends, and family... Considering that,\NI simply couldn't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.33,0:19:23.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,To be honest about the Hero Leo...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.88,0:19:27.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I don't bear him any ill will.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.54,0:19:30.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Might I ask why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.58,0:19:35.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,He is a hero. He exists to protect humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.46,0:19:41.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't fault him for doing just that:\Nfighting an invader attacking humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.38,0:19:47.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,He may have put a stop to my plans,\Nbut he was not wrong to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.63,0:19:51.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The fault lay with us, the aggressors in this war.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.58,0:19:54.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I see her differently now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.13,0:19:59.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,She's kind. A loving Queen who cares for her people.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.25,0:20:05.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yet she became an evil conquerer\Nto provide for her beloved subjects.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.42,0:20:08.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,She must have wondered\Nif she was doing the right thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.67,0:20:13.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,She must have been assailed by anxiety,\Nunspeakable despair, and ever-present worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.67,0:20:18.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And then someone brought\Nabout the greatest despair of all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.71,0:20:22.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Me, the Hero Leo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.54,0:20:25.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What about you, Onyx?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.96,0:20:26.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.75,0:20:28.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Why did you join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.08,0:20:33.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Did humanity betray you?\NDo you wish to put an end to this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.46,0:20:37.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Or have you simply come seeking a place to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.17,0:20:40.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I wish to hear your motivation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.63,0:20:43.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.46,0:20:47.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,This is why I hate going out drinking with colleagues.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.33,0:20:52.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We were shooting the shit, then suddenly\Ngot into a serious topic where I have to be honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.33,0:20:55.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It'd be easy to lie,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.29,0:20:58.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,but she's just opened her heart to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.79,0:21:02.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If I deceived her further, she'd be even\Nmore upset when I revealed who I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.75,0:21:07.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No, that wasn't it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.92,0:21:09.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I just don't want to lie to her anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.08,0:21:14.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Not as part of any strategy, but because\NI genuinely want to support her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.79,0:21:17.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Especially now that I know\Nshe just wants to save her home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.17,0:21:18.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.29,0:21:22.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Right, I suppose I should tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.58,0:21:26.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll tell her who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.63,0:21:30.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll apologize for the deception,\Nthen tell her how much I want to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.21,0:21:34.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Your Highness, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.79,0:21:35.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.46,0:21:36.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No, Echidna, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.33,0:21:37.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.17,0:21:41.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Your Highness, I finally found you....
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.21,0:21:43.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Generals?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.46,0:21:45.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's real bad! We got a problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.38,0:21:48.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,H-here...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.00,0:21:52.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm going on a journey.\NPlease don't come looking for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.29,0:21:54.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Shadowless General Mernes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.21,0:21:58.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I have failed to properly train my troops\Nand will be taking my life to make amends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.92,0:22:00.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Dragon General Edvard.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.17,0:22:03.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,WHAT?!
